    </p>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      You can try accessing the service later.
    </p>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      If you have any questions, email us at <a class="govuk-link" href="mailto:becomingateacher@digital.education.gov.uk?subject=Register%20trainee%20teachers%20support">becomingateacher@digital.education.gov.uk</a>.
    </p>

  </div>

</div>

{% endblock %}
